Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮酱～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽乃呢  还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗  没嘉宾根本撑不了两小时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记一切去唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为弄到票了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回去了  所以这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮小姐似乎想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为约好了…的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人多得厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部…都是由绮的歌迷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常感谢他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…高兴程度是99%吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只有冬弥君来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥和彰君  美咲也都送了票
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是在为我们着想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不需要在乎那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Merry  Christmas  冬弥君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me…Merry…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  立刻就去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥君也快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联络解禁了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮小姐  赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们也走吧  没人会来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后开始真的要忙了  我们都是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你周围的所有人都是你的对手…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立场…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是在说由绮的转变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为由绮会原谅你的花心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她不能原谅自己是花心的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么突然说起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了  还有另一个对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎连歌神都被由绮迷住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我和理奈只是为赢他  而走到现在的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌是奴隶  是道具  他必须臣服于我们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我或许是输了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮却不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被允许侍奉他  被他摆弄被他斥责
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能与他一起嬉戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔挑起战争  然后击败他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白吗  今天的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想唱歌  连一秒都不能停下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有歌声陪伴的话  不唱歌的话就会死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮不就是歌的恋人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  这是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不唱歌也不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是观众却得到了这样的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是  青年  你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让所有听到歌声的人感受到这种错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是职业歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是森川由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青年  你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是对手是我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会有点怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊  找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冬弥那里…是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君他去演唱会了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经结束了吧  或许是去喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君的爸爸怎么会一个人去那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在家的话去了也没用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不是拜访人家的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我已经说过会去拜访了  对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脚已经好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能推动车了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是多亏了你  非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对冬弥没有这么客气过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七濑君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥称呼你是用名字的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后也请你多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一场雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  时间…去演唱会的话也是理所当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候就在这等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:17:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么时候  刚刚来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有等你  只是刚好到了附近的朋友家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起你简历上的地址是这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友不在家  当然是女孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和男朋友去约会了  因为是平安夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就来看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  不好意思  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道现在几点吗  我家人会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  本来是想送给朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在  所以就送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕就不需要了吧  你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能让手这么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸这么冷的女孩子回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷得我都流眼泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会打什么主意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:18:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为做这种事我就会感动  什么都原谅你对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以期待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别傻了  我才不会给你什么  汗倒是一大把
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  我想你还是稍微减一下量比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减…说减肥啦  而且根本不需要减
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是由绮？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这位是由绮的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮…小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:20:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪比藤井大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我听说是同年的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？同年？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的票
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步的话我才不去  这种鬼天气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  遥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一首歌终于看到了大热的前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由松山芽乃小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  你没事吧  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把伞…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麻奈忘了带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么麻奈会去冬弥的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥  你爸爸他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.52,0:24:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的空白页
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.99,0:24:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有填满
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.26,0:24:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album

